  "rationale": "<p>Choice A is correct. The first line has slope (0 \u2212 5)/(10 \u2212 0) = \u22121/2 and y-intercept 5, so its equation is y = -x/2 + 5. The second line is y = 2. Setting -x/2 + 5 = 2 gives x = 6, so the solution is (6, 2).</p>",
